ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I will strongly recommend this course to another student who has interest in analysis. It is a very interesting course and indeed a very good training to help us think more logically.
It is a good course worth taking.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I learned a lot of useful 'tricks' to prove theorems which are especially helpful to my research of control theory, because we often need to prove things. The course also sharpens my logic thinking and intuition. After I learned this course, I can understand the exact meaning of many terms appeared in the papers more deeply.
It helps me build the logic thinking.
